{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxItem","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"Layouts","text":"Layouts","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional helper texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"reversed","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": like the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" layout but with a trailing checkbox indicator and a leading optional image"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Indicator-states","text":"Indicator states","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The checkbox indicator has three available states:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"selected","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"unselected","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If you are looking for a checkbox component with three states, use instead ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Particular-cases","text":"Particular cases","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","isActive":true},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"text":" flag is risen.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In addition, the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","isActive":true},{"text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet but this component must not be considered","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"as disabled.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component does not follow the right-to-left (RTL) \/ left-to-right (LTR) mode returned by the system as it could have some meaning"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to have for example the indicator in trailing position for LTR mode and vice versa."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, if the component has an icon in leading position (RTL mode) or in trailing position (LTR), the content of the icon is never changed."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It could lead to a loss of meaning or semantics in the icon. Thus a specific flag can be used to flip the icon content whatever the layout direction is."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It prevents the user do implement its own rules to flip or not image."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","text":"Accessibility considerations","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}]},{"type":"text","text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom checkbox trait."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Forbidden-by-design","text":"Forbidden by design","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component.","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component."}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Code-samples","text":"Code samples","type":"heading"},{"code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected checkbox","    @Published var isOn: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Hello world\")","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Hello world\", isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, and an helper text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Bazinga!\", helper: \"Doll-Dagga Buzz-Buzz Ziggety-Zag\")","","    \/\/ A trailing checkbox with a label, an helper text and an icon.","    \/\/ The reversed layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn,","                     label: \"We live in a fabled world\",","                     helper: \"Of dreaming boys and wide-eyed girls\",","                     isReversed: true,","                     icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"))","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Hello world\")","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Hello world\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Hello world\", isReadyOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you want to manage the RTL mode quite easily and switch your layouts (flip image, indicator in RTL leading i.e. in the right):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    @Environment(\\.layoutDirection) var layoutDirection","","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $selection,","                     labelText: \"Cocorico !\",","                     icon: Image(systemName: \"figure.handball\"),","                     flipIcon: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft,","                     isInversed: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft)"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Suggestions","text":"Suggestions","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"According to the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/09d860-checkbox\/t\/14bf4bd854"},{"type":"text","text":", the checkbox by default must be used in unselected state."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation","text":"Design documentation","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/09d860-checkbox"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"2.1.0 (Figma component design version)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Version","style":"note","type":"aside"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.12.0","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Since","style":"note","type":"aside"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckboxitem"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships"}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Structure","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxItem"}],"modules":[{"name":"OUDSComponents"}],"symbolKind":"struct","title":"OUDSCheckboxItem","role":"symbol","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents16OUDSCheckboxItemV","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxItem"}]},"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem"},{"text":" proposes layouts to add in your views some checkboxes components with labels and icons.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If you want to use a checkbox with only an indicator prefer instead ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\